problem:
What is the number of square centimeters in the area of this trapezoid?

[asy]
defaultpen(linewidth(0.7));
draw((0,0)--(27,0)--(15,9)--(0,9)--cycle);
label("5 cm",(21,4.5),NE);
label("5 cm",(7.5,9),N);
